– CP-SNARKs for matrix multiplication that achieve optimal proving complexity.

4) A codebase written in C\${\textbackslash}mathsf\{++\}\$ for highly composable zkSNARKs with commit-and-prove capabilities\${\textasciicircum}*\$.

