ackslash}mathcal\{O\}\}(S+T)\$, which is significantly more space efficient than a monolithic SNARK, which requires space \${\textbackslash}tilde\{{\textbackslash}mathcal\{O\}\}(S {\textbackslash}cdot T)\$.Major update. Better presentation, full implementation and evaluation},
	urldate = {2023-07-14},
	author = {Bünz, Benedikt and Maller, Mary and Mishra, Pratyush and Tyagi, Nirvan and Vesely, Psi},
	keywords = {aggregate proofs, aggregate signatures, bilinear pairings, inner pairing product, structure-preserving cryptography},
}

